title: Spice and Wolf SCANS Books (light novels) 1-7
description:
I noticed all the other Spice and Wolf books up here were translated by unofficial organizations, and the official translations are soooo much better. Especially if you're weird like me and like to quote the books. So I'm uploading the official scans, 1-7! Hope you all enjoy!
PLEASE seed and comment, and if you know where I can get the rest in scans, please message me!
~Thanks~
